                        <p>At various locations on the Site, such as when you contact us, register to use the Site, log-in to a password protected area, place an online order or make a purchase through the Site, we may request or provide you with the option to supply us with certain personally identifiable information. As part of creating an account on the Site, you may also be requested to provide questions and secret answers, which we use to help verify your identity and assist in resetting your password. If you do not want your personally identifiable information collected, please do not submit it to us. Please keep in mind that if you do not submit personally identifiable information that is requested of you, you may be unable to access certain locations and features on the Site. When you provide us with personally identifiable information, we may use that information to better understand your needs and for the purpose of operating and improving the Site and our service offerings, programs and your user experience. We may also use that information to contact you, for example, to answer a question or respond to a comment you have submitted.</p>
                        <p>
                            Whenever you provide Rosyblue with personally identifiable information, Rosyblue may use this information to send out communications to you about itself and its products and services, including but not restricted to information of new promotions, surveys, contests, sweepstakes or product or service updates. Rosyblue may also use your personally identifiable information to improve and customize the Web Site's content, layout, products and services.
                            Additionally, if you contact one of our diamond and jewelry offices (and provide personally identifiable information to the office) or submit a request or inquiry through our Web Site, Rosyblue will use your personally identifiable information to respond to your request or inquiry and to update you with any other information that we believe may be of your interest.
                        </p>
